    "ML for anomaly Detection in NFV Description of the problemAnomaly detection is an old problem, well investigated in the literature [55].",
    "In NFV, the anomaly/fault detection has become a top priority for achieving the benefits promised by this technique.",
    "In fact, network function chains are more performance stringent than common IT applications.",
    "Detecting preliminary symptoms of service degradation is thus crucial to avoid Service Level Agreement (SLA) violation.",
    "Anomaly detection in a NFV environment consists on reporting in a timely manner any abnormal condition in an NFV service."
